---
title: Moroccan Chicken & Baby Broccoli Couscous with Almonds & Lemon Yoghurt
description: We love the way honey caramelises in a pan, lending a crispy, sticky finish to chicken. We’ve used chicken thigh here because it packs a fantastic flavour, remains moist as it cooks and complements the bed of delicious roast veggie couscous that comes with it.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the currants in this recipe with flaked almonds due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just
as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66299e8b4973a916e18c111e-b5a1cce3.jpeg
